@startuml
title Registry Governance & Identity Model (Dual Gate + Ownership Mapping Enforcement + Transparency)
left to right direction

' =========================
' DARK MODE REVIEW THEME
' =========================

skinparam backgroundColor #121417
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName JetBrains Mono
skinparam defaultFontColor #f3f5f7
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 90

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #26313c
  BorderColor #7c8b9b
  FontColor #ffffff
  RoundCorner 10
  BackgroundColor<<Guard>> #3a3528
  BorderColor<<Guard>> #d2be7b
}

skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #1b2128
  BorderColor #5f6a75
  FontColor #ffffff
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #25303a
  BorderColor #7c8b9b
  FontColor #ffffff
}

skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #342b40
  BorderColor #b492d8
  FontColor #ffffff
}

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #2b3742
  BorderColor #98a7b8
  FontColor #ffffff
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #2a3138
  BorderColor #8b98a6
  FontColor #f3f5f7
}

skinparam ArrowColor #79b8ff
skinparam ArrowFontColor #f3f5f7

actor "Namespace Owner" as Owner
actor "Submission Requester\n(anyone)" as Requester
actor "Registry Admin" as Admin
actor "Launcher / Consumer" as Client

package "Ownership Anchor" #2c2438 {
  cloud "SteamID64 Namespace" as NS
}

package "External References (Not Authoritative Storage)" #2c2438 {
  cloud "Source Repo\n(GitHub)" as GH
  cloud "Steam Workshop" as SW
}

package "Canonical Publisher (CI Domain)" #24372d {
  component "CI Provenance Gate" as CIG <<Guard>>
  component "CI Provenance Manifest\n(refs + hashes + build metadata)" as SRM <<Guard>>
}

package "Registry Governance Plane" #1f2b36 {
  database "Namespace Record" as NR
  database "Namespace Ownership Mapping Index\n(active snapshot)" as NBI
  database "Namespace Ownership Mapping History\n(GitHub owner + Steam publisher aliases)" as NBH
  database "Version Ownership Mapping Snapshots\n(immutable per version)" as VOMS
  database "Version Integrity Tuple Store\n(immutable per version)" as VITS
  database "Mod Record" as MR
  database "Version Record\n(Immutable)" as VR
  database "Version Status\n(Mutable flags)" as VS
  database "Artifact Archive\n(Content-addressed cache)" as AR
  database "Source + Asset Archive\n(Git snapshot archive)" as SA
  database "Transparency Log\n(append-only hash-chained events)" as TL

  component "Ownership Mapping\nCheck" as IB <<Guard>>
  component "Ownership Mapping Update\nPolicy" as BUP <<Guard>>
  component "Namespace Identity\nMatch Check" as NIM <<Guard>>
  component "Dependency DAG\nLinter" as DAG <<Guard>>
  component "Version Tuple\nConsistency Check" as VTC <<Guard>>
  component "Registry Verification Gate" as RVG <<Guard>>
  component "Artifact + Source Fetch +\nHash Verifier" as AFV <<Guard>>
  component "Automated Review Gate" as AutoRev <<Guard>>
  component "Manual Review Gate" as ManualRev <<Guard>>
  component "Append-Only\nVersion Store" as AOVS <<Guard>>
  component "Compromise Response\nController" as CRC <<Guard>>
}

Owner -[#7ecbff]-> NS : prove namespace ownership
NS -[#7ecbff]-> IB : identity assertion
IB -[#7ecbff]-> NR : namespace anchor

NR -[#f5c57a]-> NBH : ownership transfer allowed
Admin -[#f5c57a]-> BUP : authorize ownership mapping updates
BUP -[#f5c57a]-> NBH : append alias/transfer entries
BUP -[#9de37e]-> NBI : update active ownership mapping snapshot
BUP -[#9de37e]-> TL : append ownership mapping update event

NR -[#9de37e]-> MR : namespace -> mod mapping

GH -[#b492d8]-> CIG : source reference
SW -[#b492d8]-> CIG : workshop artifact reference
CIG -[#9de37e]-> SRM : emit CI provenance manifest

Requester -[#7ecbff]-> RVG : submit release request\n(namespace, mod, version, refs,\nlogged-in identities)
SRM -[#9de37e]-> RVG : candidate manifest
RVG -[#9de37e]-> RVG : verify CI provenance
RVG -[#9de37e]-> NIM : verify GitHub + Steam identity match
NIM -[#9de37e]-> NBI : verify active ownership mapping snapshot
NIM -[#9de37e]-> IB : verify namespace ownership mapping
NIM -[#9de37e]-> VOMS : persist version ownership mapping snapshot
RVG -[#9de37e]-> DAG : validate exact dependency DAG
RVG -[#9de37e]-> AFV : verify hashes + reference consistency
AFV -[#b492d8]-> SW : fetch artifact bytes by ref
AFV -[#b492d8]-> GH : fetch source snapshot by ref
AFV -[#9de37e]-> AR : persist verified artifact bytes
AFV -[#9de37e]-> SA : persist verified source snapshot
AFV -[#9de37e]-> VTC : provide digests + refs
VOMS -[#9de37e]-> VTC : provide ownership mapping snapshot id
SRM -[#9de37e]-> VTC : provide CI provenance id
VTC -[#9de37e]-> VITS : persist immutable version tuple

DAG -[#9de37e]-> AOVS : graph validation result
RVG -[#9de37e]-> AOVS : admission passed
AOVS -[#9de37e]-> VR : append immutable version record
AOVS -[#9de37e]-> TL : append admission event
VR -[#f5c57a]-> VS : initialize status = pending_review
VS -[#9de37e]-> AutoRev : queue post-admission checks
AutoRev -[#9de37e]-> VS : mark active (pass path)
AutoRev -[#f5c57a]-> ManualRev : escalate flagged cases
Admin -[#f5c57a]-> ManualRev : perform moderation
ManualRev -[#f5c57a]-> VS : set active/deprecated/banned
ManualRev -[#9de37e]-> TL : append moderation event

Admin -[#c87878]-> CRC : report compromised identity mapping
CRC -[#c87878]-> NBI : freeze active ownership mapping
CRC -[#c87878]-> VS : quarantine historical versions by mapping
CRC -[#9de37e]-> TL : append compromise event

Client -[#7ecbff]-> VR : resolve public version metadata
Client -[#7ecbff]-> VS : check status flags
Client -[#7ecbff]-> VITS : fetch immutable version tuple
Client -[#7ecbff]-> AR : fetch artifact by digest
Client -[#7ecbff]-> SA : fetch source snapshot (audit/repro)
Client -[#9de37e]-> VOMS : verify version ownership mapping snapshot
Client -[#9de37e]-> VITS : verify registry/archive/mapping tuple consistency

GH -[dashed,#c87878]-> VR : direct write forbidden
SW -[dashed,#c87878]-> VR : direct write forbidden

Owner -[hidden]-> Requester
Requester -[hidden]-> Admin
Admin -[hidden]-> Client
GH -[hidden]- SW
CIG -[hidden]- SRM
IB -[hidden]- NIM
NIM -[hidden]- DAG
DAG -[hidden]- RVG
RVG -[hidden]- AOVS
AOVS -[hidden]- AFV
NBI -[hidden]- TL
VOMS -[hidden]- VR
VITS -[hidden]- VOMS

note bottom
- Dual gate: CI provenance gate + registry verification gate
- No custom owner-signature mechanism in v1
- Namespace identity is bound to GitHub repo ownership + Steam publisher identity
- Ownership mapping mismatches hard-fail admission
- Ownership transfers are represented in alias history + active ownership mapping snapshot
- Each version stores an immutable ownership mapping snapshot for runtime validation
- Each version stores an immutable integrity tuple for cross-store consistency
- Version records immutable append-only; status mutable (active/deprecated/banned)
- New records start pending_review and are not publicly consumable
- Deprecation warns; ban/quarantine blocks execution
- Transparency log records ownership mapping/status/admission/compromise events
end note

@enduml
